A two-year-old girl drowned in a pool at a home on Andries Pretorious Road in Pietermaritzburg on Tuesday. Paramedics believe that the child was playing near the swimming pool when she fell in. She was pulled out of the pool by one of her family members after they found her floating in the pool. ER24 Spokesperson Robert McKenzie said on arrival paramedics were shown the body of the child and they found that she showed no signs of life. Sadly, she was declared dead on the scene&#8221;.-TNA Reporter